ss.org.il/publication/suicide-bombings-worldwide-in-2019-signs-of-decline-following-the-military-defeat-of-the-islamic-state/] 12 bombers in Jan.-Feb. 2020,[https://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2020/02/hts-utilizes-suicide-bombings-against-advancing-regime-forces.php] total of at least 455 suicide bombers killed</ref> and 246 rebel [[Military use of children|child soldiers]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.hrw.org/news/2014/06/22/syria-armed-groups-send-children-battle |title=Syria: Armed Groups Send Children into Battle |publisher=HRW |date=2014-06-22 |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415070738/http://www.hrw.org/news/2014/06/22/syria-armed-groups-send-children-battle |archive-date=2015-04-15 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2015/7/15/syrias-kurdish-militia-still-using-child-soldiers|title=Dozens of IS group child soldiers killed in Syria|author=Al-Araal-Jadeed staff|work=alaraby|accessdate=28 October 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203164133/http://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2015/7/15/syrias-kurdish-militia-still-using-child-soldiers|archive-date=3 February 2016|url-status=live}}</ref> that have been killed in the conflict. Additionally, 930 foreign pro-Kurdish fighters died.<ref>http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=152189</ref><ref name=YPGforeigners>26 Turks,[https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/NewsReports/565298-outlawed-turkish-party-establishes-syria-battalion] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730212802/https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/NewsReports/565298-outlawed-turkish-party-establishes-syria-battalion |date=2017-07-30 }}[https://kyleorton1991.files.wordpress.com/2017/07/2017-08-17-pyd-pkk-foreign-fighters.pdf] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190218021551/https://kyleorton1991.files.wordpress.com/2017/07/2017-08-17-pyd-pkk-foreign-fighters.pdf |date=2019-02-18 }}[https://anfenglish.com/news/thousands-bid-farewell-to-bog-fighter-and-hpg-g