i girl killed by indirect fire from Syria |publisher=Google.com |date=2012-09-08 |accessdate=2013-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514014851/https://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5gUvb9stZC-Dym3s40BBeiMg0GYLQ?docId=CNG.0f87b2c4d6a2783e2397f8764776ea9c.6c1 |archive-date=2013-05-14 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/syriahroe/posts/433396686768675|title=Reef Dimashq|publisher=|accessdate=25 October 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203164133/https://www.facebook.com/syriahroe/posts/433396686768675|archive-date=3 February 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Lebanon]] || 42<ref name=\"shuhadanationality\"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Apr-07/169560-lebanese-killed-15-wounded-after-bus-hit-on-lebanon-syria-border.ashx#axzz1zEDfTuxH |title=Lebanon-Syria border bus attack kills 7, wounds 21 |publisher=Dailystar.com.lb |date= |accessdate=8 July 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723064319/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Apr-07/169560-lebanese-killed-15-wounded-after-bus-hit-on-lebanon-syria-border.ashx#axzz1zEDfTuxH |archive-date=23 July 2012 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://af.reuters.com/article/topNews/idAFJOE86602Y20120707 |title=Syria's fighting spills into Lebanon, five killed |publisher=Af.reuters.com |date=9 February 2009 |accessdate=8 July 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006183949/http://af.reuters.com/article/topNews/idAFJOE86602Y20120707 |archive-date=6 October 2014 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Reuters |url=http://www.jpost.com/MiddleEast/Article.aspx?id=276911 |title=Three dead after more Syrian shells hit Lebanon |publisher=Jpost.com |date= |accessdate=2013-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120711025414/http://www.jpost.com/MiddleEast/Article.aspx?id=276911 |archive-date=2012-07-11 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http: